# Deployment Package

This directory contains the MVP deployment handoff for `{{ spec.project.name }}`.
It is intentionally local-first and does **not** flash real hardware or deploy to
cloud infrastructure automatically.

## Local validation before handoff

```bash
cd {{ spec.project.name }}
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pytest -q
python simulation/simulator.py
python -m http.server 8080
```

Open `dashboard/index.html` after the HTTP server starts.

## Production-readiness checklist

- Confirm every sensor mapping against physical hardware datasheets.
- Review every reflex threshold with a qualified domain engineer.
- Run the simulator with site-specific scenarios.
- Keep API keys and secrets outside this repository and ZIP package.
- Perform independent safety review before connecting actuators to real machinery.
